{"id": 231283518, "title": "6 of the Best Pull-Up Bars for Your Home Gym in 2024", "text": "Pull-ups are an effective and efficient workout because they target your back, shoulders, arms and core using your body weight. Whether you're working toward doing a pull-up for the first time or you've been doing them for years, an at-home pull-up bar is a great addition to your home gym. Invest in one of the best pull-up bars to improve your pull-up form from home. Pull-up bars come in various styles, including doorway-, wall- and ceiling-mounted, and freestanding bars. Each style has different benefits. A doorway pull-up bar is cheaper and ideal if you have a smaller living space. Mounted pull-up bars are drilled into the wall or ceiling and are more permanent. If you have more space and want a versatile option that can be used for other exercises like knee raises, push-ups, or tricep dips, you can go for freestanding pull-up bars, also known as power towers. Regardless of your budget and space, you can find a great pull-up bar for your home gym. I've put together this list of some of the best pull-up bars available for home use, based on hundreds of customer reviews, brand reputability and durability. Best pull-up bars for your home gym in 2024", "summary": "Get your body-weight workouts at home with our picks of the best pull-up bars for your home gym.", "url": "https://www.cnet.com/health/fitness/best-pull-up-bars/", "image": "https://www.cnet.com/a/img/resize/d33880ad84721d597852ca4a7d84e56aa1d0036d/hub/2024/06/04/cf3af09e-8844-4a22-b1e3-8cf95be5972d/best-pullup-bars.jpg?auto=webp&fit=crop&height=675&width=1200", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-08 14:46:12", "author": "Giselle Castro-Sloboda", "authors": ["Giselle Castro-Sloboda"], "language": "en", "source_country": "US", "sentiment": 0.69}